[[Skeleton]]s are [[undead]] [[monster]]s that can be assigned as tasks at combat level 15 by various slayer masters. They are often found in cemeteries and dungeons. A good strategy to kill them is to use melee with a weapon with [[Crush weapons|crush]] bonuses (such as a [[Viggora's chainmace]]) and a [[salve amulet]] or [[salve amulet (e)]], due to their low defense against that style of attack.

Another strategy to kill them would be with magic, using the [[Crumble Undead]] spell on them.

